contentrichtext.text: {{Wiktionary|java|Java}} '''[[Java]]''' is the world's most populous island, located in Indonesia. '''Java''' may also refer to: {{TOC right}} ==Places== ===Indonesia=== *[[Java Sea]], north of the island of Java *[[Java Trench]], a subduction zone trench west of the island of Java ===United
